OL,5, Sub-postmasters wrongfully prosecuted  
OL,6, by the Post Office had their lives     
OL,7, "utterly destroyed" by the scandal,    
OL,8, lawyers acting for them have said.     
OL,10,FHundreds of people were convicted after
OL,11,Ffaulty Horizon software flagged false  
OL,12,Fdiscrepancies in accounts.             
OL,14,FAn ongoing public inquiry has been     
OL,15,Flooking at how the court cases were    
OL,16,Fbrought against sub-postmasters.       
OL,18,FOne lawyer said this phase of the probe
OL,19,Fhad "pulled back the curtain" on the   
OL,20,Fscandal.                               
